---
layout: layouts/base.njk
templateClass: no-footer
---

<style>

  .cursor {
    height: 0;
    width: 0;
    display: none;
  }

  .window-content p {
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .cursor-animate {
    width: 25px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: cursor 4s linear infinite;
  }

  .cursor-wrapper-clouds svg:nth-child(1n) {
    fill: var(--color-text);
    animation: clouds 2s linear infinite;
    animation-direction: alternate;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  @keyframes clouds {
    0% {
      transform: skew(15deg, 15deg);
    } 100% {
      transform: skew(0);
    }
  }           

  @keyframes cursor {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
    } 100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .cursor-wrapper-mail svg {
    fill: var(--color-text);
    animation: 2s mail linear infinite;
    animation-direction: alternate;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  @keyframes mail {
    0% {
      transform: scale(0.4);
    } 100% {
      transform: scale(0.9, 0.8);
    }
  }

  .cursor-wrapper-cursors svg {
    fill: var(--color-text);
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    animation: wiggle 3s ease-in infinite;
    animation-direction: alternate;
  }

  .window-cascade-title .window-content {
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    min-height: 300px;

    .inputs {
      margin-top: 70px;
    }
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 35px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .window-cascade-post {
    min-height: 15rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    position: relative;

    .notes-list-title {
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .window-content {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 15rem;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .notes-list-item-index {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      right: 0;
    }
  }

  @keyframes wiggle {
    0% {
      transform: rotate(220deg);
    } 50% {
      transform: rotate(225deg);
    } 60% {
      transform: rotate(210deg);
    } 70% {
      transform: rotate(215deg);
    } 80% {
      transform: rotate(220deg);
    } 100% {
      transform: rotate(220deg);
    }
  }
</style>

<svg class="cursor" width="85" height="134" viewBox="0 0 85 134" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <g id="icon-cursor">
      <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M0 117.162V0L85.0007 85.0022H35.2733L32.2593 85.9093L0 117.162Z" fill="white"/>
      <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M66.6229 122.095L40.1862 133.325L5.85156 52.2003L32.8822 40.8389L66.6229 122.095Z" fill="white"/>
      <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M56.8419 117.116L43.3193 122.778L20.5859 68.8313L34.0866 63.1616L56.8419 117.116Z" fill="black"/>
      <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M7.33594 17.6098V99.4589L29.1086 78.4918L32.2473 77.4749H67.2126L7.33594 17.6098Z" fill="black"/>
    </g>
  </defs>
</svg>

<div class="grid">
  <div class="window window-cascade-title grid-column-12">
    <div class="window-title"> 
      <h1>The Cascade</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="window-content window-content-wrapper">
      <p>This newsletter is all about the past, present, and future of CSS. The properties! The color spaces! The weird layout hacks! All the latest web dev drama! Thereâ€™s so much to cover every week but each edition is short and sweet, easily scannable over a morning coffee.</p> <p>Sign up below for updates every Saturday or subscribe <a href="/cascadefeed.xml">via RSS</a>.</p>

      <form
        action="https://buttondown.email/api/emails/embed-subscribe/cascade"
        method="post"
        target="popupwindow"
        onsubmit="window.open('https://buttondown.email/cascade', 'popupwindow')"
        class="embeddable-buttondown-form"
      >
        <div class="inputs">
          <input type="email" name="email" id="bd-email" placeholder="Email address" />
          <input type="submit" value="Subscribe" />
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="grid">
  {% for post in collections.cascade | reverse %}
    <a class="window window-link window-cascade-post grid-column-4 {{loop.index}}" href="{{ post.url }}">
      <div class="window-content window-content-wrapper">
        {% set total = loop.length - loop.index %}
        <div class="notes-list-item-index">{{total}}</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="notes-list-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
          <p class="notes-list-extract">{{ post.data.extract }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
